\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]] (It seems like a pointless debate is
heating up...)

When you look into someone's eyes, you can
understand their true nature. That's what the old
man used to say to me over and over again.

I still haven't embodied those words of the old
man. After all, everyone around me either has eyes
filled with flattery and insincerity, or they look
at my appearance with disgust and hostility.

Hmmm... Does this mean that I understand someone's
true nature? No, that can't be right... What the
old man wanted to say wasn't something like that.

But, I... have finally embodied it. The old man's
words were right. I could tell just by looking
into their eyes.

On that day... I came to a certain television
station, half for a meeting and half to check out
the new announcer, MIsaki-chan.

A woman wearing a motorcycle suit jumped into my
field of vision as soon as I got off the elevator.
For a moment, I thought she might be a suspicious
person or a dangerous woman.

I first looked at her face to confirm her
appearance, as usual. Then, the woman also turned
her face towards me, so our gazes met.

As soon as I looked into her eyes, I understood.
Ah, this person is the complete opposite of me.
And it seems like she has lived a proper life
until now.

......It was shocking. I never thought there would
be someone like this... In the dirty side of the
entertainment industry, where I have been
completely tainted, I honestly felt that way.
And I immediately came to this thought.
I want to completely defile you.

How exhilarating would it be if I were to stain
that innocent face with filthy pleasure and bring
you down to the same stage as me?

If it were an ordinary guy, it would just end with
thoughts. Even if they could do it, they would
just write about it in their dark fantasies and be
satisfied, and that would be the end.

However, I am different from those small fries. I
have status, fame, and a vast network of people.
Yes... I have the absolute power to make fantasies
come true.

So I immediately took action. While preparing,
every time I remembered this person, my dick would
be fully erect without fail. My dick was
definitely yearning for them.

Ah, it was such a fun time. It felt like I went
back to my middle school days when all I could
think about was sex, even though lately I've been
having sex while yawning.

However, that time was finally coming to an end.
Surely... the days of spending such hopeful and
fulfilling moments will never come again. Thinking
that way, I feel a little bit of sadness, but...
